snippet.title: Greg Raiz
snippet.description:
I'm passionate about improving people's lives through the power of technology and design.  I'm an angel investor, mentor, and entrepreneur. Subscribe to the channel if you're interested in business, technology and products. 

For startups pitching, I have additional info on my website https://gregraiz.com and for people with questions I welcome you to join my discord server for ad-hoc discussions.  https://discord.gg/U9CdduE
